    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The carmen employed by the\nWashington Water Power company\nhave petitioned the company for an\nincrease in pay and modification of\ncertain rules.\n\n\nA meeting has been called by the\ncompany at the car barn at 3\no'clock this afternoon and another\nat s tonight, when the company will\nsubmit its answer.\n\n\nThe argument of the men is that\nthey cannot live and maintain\nfamilies on the wages now paid.\nThe recent revision of their scale\ngave them shorter hours but did\nnot affect the question of living."
    }
  ]
